# how-i-did

1) add user in DSM control panel so that home directory etc is mapped

2) Install debian-chroot from synocommunity packages: 
https://markpith.wordpress.com/2015/10/26/debian-chroot-on-synology-nas/

3) Install Cloud Station for Dropbox functionality on home dir

